 Peter Fox , from Liverpool , was arrested at Euston Station in London this morning on suspicion of the murders of Bernadette , 57 , and Sarah Fox , 27 , following a nationwide manhunt .
Detectives released CCTV images of the 26-year-old leaving Liverpool Lime Street at 8.18 pm on Wednesday .
The body of his sister was found by police on Thursday night , just half a mile away .